{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, they employed a clustering algorithm to examine various patterns of cluster interaction [26].",
    "Turabieh et al.",
    "introduced a method that enhances the Harris Hawkes optimization (HHO) approach.",
    "This method addresses the issue of premature convergence by managing population diversity.",
    "They also employed the k-nearest neighbor (kNN) method as a strategy for clustering, which allowed them to monitor the performance of HHO in adjusting population diversity [27]."
  ]
}